                <h1>Enhancing Background Knowledge for ELLs</h1>
                <p>Building background knowledge for English Language Learners (ELLs) is essential for their success. It involves connecting new information to students’ prior experiences and cultural contexts. Effective strategies include using visuals, storytelling, and collaborative activities that promote engagement, helping ELLs make meaningful connections and improve comprehension.</p>
